snippet.title: Public & Cargo Transportation I Feature Highlights #3 I Cities: Skylines II
snippet.description:
How do citizens and goods get from A to B? VIA PUBLIC & CARGO TRANSPORTATION! DUH! The third Feature Highlight video is all about it, so pull out your transit passes and let's head over to Knowledge City!

Footage captured In-Game is not final and might change in time for release.

Pre-Order Cities: Skylines II NOW!
